## Context
To auto-generate migrations, we need comprehensive schema introspection that captures ALL metadata about existing tables, columns, constraints, and indexes.

## Current State
- Basic introspection exists in `sqlmodel-schema/src/introspect.rs`
- Covers: tables, columns, basic types
